title: Percentage of U.S. population who are veterans in 2018 , by age and gender
summary: You are viewing a chart of multi-line type with 2 lines denoting Male, and Female. The y axis indicates the Percentage of population and the x axis indicates Year.
Overall Male is rapidly increasing, Female is roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The ranking of the lines from topmost to botommmost is as follows: 1. Male, and lastly, 2. Female.
Throughout the period, Male generally had the highest Percentage of population relative to others with an average of 20.65, and it reached its maximum at 75_years_and_over with a value of 45.51.
The botommost line, Female,  has a mean of 1.27, and peaked at 55_to_64_years.
